blogPost.excerpt:
Today AD brings you to sunny La Jolla, California on the coast of the Pacific Ocean to tour the art-filled, modernist home of superstar couple Alicia Keys and Kasseem Dean (a.k.a. Swizz Beatz.) A stunning cliffside mansion by architectural designer Wallace E. Cunningham, Kasseem had the multi-level "Razor House" as his phone’s screen saver for 8 years, waiting for a day when the stars would align. Once he and his Grammy-award winning wife were able to make it their own, they set out with AD100 designer Kelly Behun to craft a home they now call their literal “Dreamland.” As for the results? “When your screen saver comes to life, it’s unbelievably crazy” says Dean.

See more of Alicia and Kasseem's home here: https://www.architecturaldigest.com/story/inside-alicia-keys-and-swizz-beatzs-art-filled-modernist-home-overlooking-the-pacific-ocean

Shop Alicia Keys and Swizz Beatz’s home style!
Take a design note from the couple whose scene-stealing seat collection includes clean-looking Mathieu Lehanneur sofas, sleek José Zanine Caldas leather chairs, and ultra-comfortable textured dining chairs:
(Similar) Orren Ellis Layla-Jayne Armless Curved Sofa with Reversible Cushions: https://fave.co/3jT0Caj
(Similar) The Citizenry San Rafael Safari Chair: https://fave.co/3bystIl
(Similar) Crate & Barrel Harper Shearling Accent Chair: https://fave.co/3q2CNkB

For a pop of color similar to the couples’ velvet tufted sectional sofa from Todd Merrill studio turn to these comparable styles:
(Similar) Article Sven Sectional: https://fave.co/3jYLXe1
(Similar) Lulu & Georgia Rivington Sofa: https://fave.co/3w5vOIs

Here's a few similar-looking rustic accents to bring a modern bohemian vibe to your space:
(Similar) Serena and Lily Teak Stool: https://fave.co/3q06mmA
(Similar) Foundry Select Fabrizia Solid Wood Accent Stool: https://fave.co/3BPwK5b
(Similar) Pottery Barn Fraiser Handcrafted Etched Vase: https://fave.co/3CLjPT6
(Similar) West Elm Ceramic Totem Vase: https://fave.co/3BI6Lw5

Love the family’s plantscapes and floral arrangements? Here’s some greenery, dried bouquets, and a planter that can be shipped right to your door:
(Similar) Bloomscape Monstera: https://fave.co/3BCT6ql
(Similar) Dried Flower Bouquet: https://fave.co/3BEkt3p
(Similar) The Sill Large Majesty Palm: https://fave.co/3jWAvzi
(Similar) Light + Ladder Vayu Planter & Tray: https://fave.co/2Y96Ds1

Create your own healing environment with these sage and oat milk-infused candles from Keys’ own line Keys Soulcare. They’re formulated with clean ingredients and hand poured to relax your mind and body.
Keys Soulcare Sage + Oat Milk Votive Candle Set: https://fave.co/3GDfEuV
Keys Soulcare Sage + Oat Milk Votive Candle: https://fave.co/3EAvvZ7

Add finishing touches with the couples’ preferred Bang & Olufsen sound systems and Alicia’s latest album:
Bang & Olufsen Silver & Grey Beosound Level Speaker: https://fave.co/2Y5xFQW
Bang & Olufsen Beosound Explore Durable Portable Wireless Bluetooth Speaker: https://fave.co/3pYuTZu
ALICIA By Alicia Keys: https://amzn.to/3buuPrV
